# Environment Variables for Comics Backend

## Required Variables

### Database
```env
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/groqtales
# or MongoDB Atlas: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/groqtales
```

### IPFS (Pinata)
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_PINATA_API_KEY=your_pinata_api_key_here
PINATA_API_SECRET=your_pinata_api_secret_here
PINATA_JWT=your_pinata_jwt_here
```

### Server
```env
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=production
CORS_ORIGIN=https://yourdomain.com
```

## Optional Variables

### NFT Minting (Optional - for on-chain comics)
```env
# Contract address for minting comics as NFTs
COMIC_NFT_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...

# Private key for minting transactions (keep secure!)
MINTING_PRIVATE_KEY=0x...

# RPC URLs for different networks
POLYGON_RPC_URL=https://polygon-rpc.com
ETHEREUM_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.infura.io/v3/YOUR_PROJECT_ID
BASE_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.base.org
ARBITRUM_RPC_URL=https://arb1.arbitrum.io/rpc
OPTIMISM_RPC_URL=https://mainnet.optimism.io
```

### Search Integration (Optional)
```env
# Elasticsearch
ELASTICSEARCH_URL=http://localhost:9200

# Algolia
ALGOLIA_APP_ID=your_app_id
ALGOLIA_API_KEY=your_api_key
```

### Authentication (Implement based on your auth system)
```env
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_here
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d
```

## Development Only
```env
NODE_ENV=development
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000
```

## Production Checklist

✅ Set `NODE_ENV=production`
✅ Configure CORS_ORIGIN to your production domain
✅ Use strong JWT_SECRET (if using JWT auth)
✅ Secure MINTING_PRIVATE_KEY (use secrets manager in production)
✅ Set up MongoDB with authentication enabled
✅ Configure backup for MongoDB
✅ Set up monitoring and logging
✅ Rate limiting configured in backend.js
✅ SSL/TLS enabled for API endpoints

## Security Notes

1. **Never commit .env files** - Add to .gitignore
2. **Use environment-specific configs** - Dev, staging, production
3. **Rotate API keys regularly** - Especially minting private keys
4. **Use secrets managers** - AWS Secrets Manager, Vault, etc.
5. **Limit API key permissions** - Pinata: only pinning permissions needed
6. **Monitor usage** - Set up alerts for unusual activity
7. **Backup private keys securely** - Offline cold storage for minting keys
